burlap.shell.command.world

Class ManualAgentsCommands

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.shell.command.world.ManualAgentsCommands

  • public class ManualAgentsCommands
extends Object
    A controller for a set of ShellCommand objects. These commands including registering manually controlled agents with a World that can play games in the world. Listing the manual agents. Setting the action selections of manual agents, and listing the currently selected actions of the manual agents. Use the -h option for help information.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
